Action from the last-16 second-leg ties, as the teams attempted to secure a passage to the quarter-finals. Fixtures included Manchester United v Liverpool at Old Trafford, and Tottenham Hotspur v Borussia Dortmund at White Hart Lane. Mark Pougatch is joined by Roy Keane and Dietmar Hamann pitchside at Old Trafford, while Jacqui Oatley is in the studio with Glenn Hoddle.
